Interface Story<I,​N extends StoryNode>

  • Type Parameters:
    N - Story nodes type StoryNode
    I - Story's node id type
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface Story<I,​N extends StoryNode>
    Represents game story
    Story must be Singleton!
